items.title: Teenage girl killed in shark attack in Australia
items.description: The 17-year-old was attacked around 100m from shore of Woormin Beach, Australian media reports.

items.title: Trump threatens to cut funding for South Africa over land policy
items.description: South Africa last month passed a law allowing the seizure of land under certain circumstances.

items.title: Car bomb blast in northern Syria kills 15 agricultural workers
items.description: Fourteen women were among those killed in the attack outside Manbij, the Syria Civil Defence says.

items.title: Spain football kiss 'stained' World Cup win, player tells trial
items.description: Luis Rubiales went on trial in Madrid on Monday over the kiss, accused of sexual assault and coercion.

items.title: Santorini on alert as tremors rattle Greek island
items.description: Authorities advise against gatherings in enclosed spaces following a flurry of seismic activity nearby.
